(% style=&amp;#34;font-family: Calibri; font-size: 0.8em&amp;#34; %)**Sato 8** [Rebecca, Contributing Editor at DailyGalaxy.com, former Head Writer at Freedom FastTrack “(% style=&amp;#34;color:#000000;&amp;#34; %)[[(% style=&amp;#34;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 0.8em&amp;#34; %)Can Changes in Sea Level Cause Periods of Mass Extinction?—A Galaxy Exclusive&amp;#62;&amp;#62;url:http://www.dailygalaxy.com/my_weblog/2008/06/changes-in-sea.html]](% style=&amp;#34;font-family: Calibri; font-size: 0.8em&amp;#34; %),” 6-19, (% style=&amp;#34;color:#000000;&amp;#34; %)[[(% style=&amp;#34;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 0.8em&amp;#34; %)http:~~/~~/www.dailygalaxy.com/my_weblog/2008/06/changes-in-sea.html&amp;#62;&amp;#62;url:http://www.dailygalaxy.com/my_weblog/2008/06/changes-in-sea.html]](% style=&amp;#34;font-family: Calibri; font-size: 0.8em&amp;#34; %)]

